        <item>
            <title>Tim Cook: 中國青年才俊令我印象深刻，很高興 Apple 產品助青年實現夢想</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/tim-cook-said-chinese-teenagers-impression-deep/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tim-cook-said-chinese-teenagers-impression-deep</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/tim-cook-said-chinese-teenagers-impression-deep/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 11:30:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299360</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 公司行政總裁 Tim Cook 今日透過微博發文，讚揚中國青年才俊的傑出表現。他表示，看到 MacBook Pro、Mac Studio 及 Apple Vision Pro 等產品協助這些年輕人追逐夢想，感到十分欣慰。發文附有與青年代表的合照，氣氛輕鬆愉快。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032540840-621x580.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032540840-621x580.jpg 621w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032540840.jpg 749w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 621px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/5524254784">Tim Cook@Weibo</a></p><p>Tim Cook 在微博中具體提到，中國青年才俊利用 Apple 產品展現創意與才華，例如用 MacBook Pro 追蹤風暴、以 Mac Studio 運行大型語言模型，甚至透過 Apple Vision Pro 教授物理學。他強調，這些實例充分展示 Apple 技術如何成為年輕人實現理想的重要工具。青年代表與 Tim Cook 交流時現場演示產品應用，最後更一同合影留念。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4ziwlp-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4ziwlp-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4ziwlp.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/5524254784">Tim Cook@Weibo</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299366" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zhf1a-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zhf1a-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zhf1a.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zhf1a-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/5524254784">Tim Cook@Weibo</a></p><p>Tim Cook 於 3 月 23 日抵達北京，展開 2025 年首次中國行程。除與青年才俊互動外，他亦參與了在釣魚台國賓館舉行的中國發展高層論壇 2025 年年會，期間被問及是否使用中國 AI 應用 DeepSeek，他回答：「當然，很棒！」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zi89q-550x580.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zi89q-550x580.jpg 550w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zi89q.jpg 853w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 550px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/5524254784">Tim Cook@Weibo</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/tim-cook-said-chinese-teenagers-impression-deep/fun-tech/">Tim Cook: 中國青年才俊令我印象深刻，很高興 Apple 產品助青年實現夢想</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
