        <item>
            <title>港安醫院檢查燈突然墜落傷及兩名醫護，全面排查同款設備確保安全</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/lighting-fall/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lighting-fall</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/lighting-fall/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 07:18:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
